f=Product/spec/custom/backlog-rules/SKILL.md · in=Backlog hygiene law: evidence-gated intake, RICE-scored prioritization (math `scripts/rice.py`, rubric honestly flagged), age-out, published next-view. backlog decision record, wish list. · p=Backlogs rot two ways: unvetted entries (no evidence) immortal entries (no age-out). make prioritization theater. skill keeps list short, cited, honestly ranked. · wu=Any item wants (intake gate)., Prioritization cadence fires (`<FILL_IN: suggested sprint/cycle>`)., item ages past limit evidence superseded. · st:/ Protocol=INTAKE (evidence citation link product's north-star metric profile `<FILL_IN: NSM product>` citation, bounced reason) SCORE (`python scripts/rice.py items.json`: Reach Impact Confidence Effort; **RICE rubric ranking carries `[reasoning-based, formula-verified]` until logical/ grounds weights**) RANK (score orders list; operator/vista strategic overrides recorded overrides, re-scored) AGE-OUT (unranked untouched `<FILL_IN: suggested days catalog default>` archived reason; re-entry needs fresh evidence, scout's re-open pattern) PUBLISH (next-`<FILL_IN: suggested 3>`-cycles view, visible Engineering vista). · in=Intake bounces kind cited: which gate failed (no evidence NSM link duplicate item X). RICE inputs estimates say so: Reach metric's data possible (cited), Impact/Confidence flagged judgment, Effort Engineering's estimate (never spec's). Confidence caps evidence ladder: opinion-level evidence (L1–2) caps Confidence `<FILL_IN: suggested 50%>` script enforces coupling. Archived deleted: age-outs keep their record reason (append-only, house pattern). published view commitment surface: changes mid-cycle recorded reasons (silent reshuffles trust backlog dies). · of=Ranked backlog (item evidence ref NSM link RICE inputs+score flag); bounce notices; age-out log; published next-view. · pr=Cite bounce; rank archive; publish stand behind it., Effort Engineering's number; Confidence capped evidence, optimism., Overrides legitimate visible strategy outrank scores, silently never. · f=NSM defined product (profile gap)? Intake still requires evidence; NSM-link waived named gap flag, profile gap goes spec's report operator. · b:with Other Skills=prd-discipline picks what ranks; opportunity-assessment feeds big items in; vista consumes published view roadmap., rice.py math rule 0.6; weights logical layer's future job.